    "name": "BOBRKUR",
    "steam_appid": 3240280,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240280/extras/7c1da25bb581b2467b3b3ad1401be3eb.avif?t=1729181976\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240280/extras_big/7c1da25bb581b2467b3b3ad1401be3eb.avif?t=1729181976 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&quot;Bobr Kur&quot;</strong> is a dynamic clicker game where players control beavers collecting resources to build a dam.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240280/extras/78d47e561a777936eb4996142402c4b4.avif?t=1729181976\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240280/extras_big/78d47e561a777936eb4996142402c4b4.avif?t=1729181976 width=800 height=456 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Each click gathers materials, and the more you collect, the more money you earn. Earned money can be spent on buying new beavers with enhanced skills, as well as various boosts like increased power or faster money generation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240280/extras/81295762e73a0a2b26da0b93ce330f8d.avif?t=1729181976\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240280/extras_big/81295762e73a0a2b26da0b93ce330f8d.avif?t=1729181976 width=800 height=452 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > These upgrades help beavers gather resources faster and in greater amounts. With new beavers and boosts, players can progress through levels quicker and help the beavers complete the dam construction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240280/extras/a22368335b7407e95a4de62dbcd31c4a.avif?t=1729181976\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240280/extras_big/a22368335b7407e95a4de62dbcd31c4a.avif?t=1729181976 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
